Package com.ibm.wala.dalvik.util

package com.ibm.wala.dalvik.util
Classes of general use with the AndroidModel.

These include mainly locationg and managing EntryPoints. The model howver is built in the androidModel-Package.

Author:
Tobias Blaschke <code@tobiasblaschke.de>
